_sText:
Cool Features:

- funky lighting
- auto-buys ammo when you enter the buyzone in the middle
- vending machine dispenses HE grenades
- randomly selects 1 of 9 songs from HL2 to play at the begining of each round

The main reason I made this map is because Ive seen so many people playing fy_iceworld and I see that map as being fairly boring and uninteresting.

I thought it would be easy to make a map that plays the same, while looking and feeling better.
